{"tid":1689694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【落TVB廣告 = 拖累品牌形象】每日洗版任務 - 誇大性能嘅 \"日立Hitachi\"","createTime":"2019-11-03T03:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T10:12:04.000Z","uid":267969,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"10d2c74396c3f9feff4b4065f577669d8c1e5205","tid":1689694,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">TVB 真係淆晒底，竟然教廣告商攬炒，封鎖顧客留言</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎手足share下面FB post俾朋友睇，<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊恥笑TVB，打擊TVB士氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心人順便like埋FB，7月底開page只係得21000 like，<span style=\"color: red;\">望住呢個數字廣告商唔會驚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/487797215410466/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F487797215410466%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=906fa2c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/487797215410466/?type=3&amp;theater</a></span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/76609886_487797218743799_2935457134311112704_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_oc=AQkrpPf2qgTdOy5AMz7IOIVVDgeVekm7-TWO-Tk3kG_yXdFO3nKciS5GsAeH3LZxH2c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=f3d80fc1c7a8927e9e9c906e231b7386&amp;oe=5E63895B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F76609886_487797218743799_2935457134311112704_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_oc%3DAQkrpPf2qgTdOy5AMz7IOIVVDgeVekm7-TWO-Tk3kG_yXdFO3nKciS5GsAeH3LZxH2c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Df3d80fc1c7a8927e9e9c906e231b7386%26oe%3D5E63895B&h=1732679b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好喇，尋日出完街，瞓醒鍵戰再上場！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個個話想TVB死，唔該拎返每日用幾秒鍵戰嘅決心出嚟</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌只開抵制TVB行動post，唔會開9up post，請順便follow我個acc<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@3 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>日立Hitachi</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HitachiHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHitachiHK%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=35ef95a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HitachiHK/</a></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaLACXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaLACXe.jpg&h=bedf3ec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">上圖：黑警冇得屌女，所以圍住LKF唔俾市民屌女</span> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>講下臭屎</strong><br />\n原來日立屢次被消委會踢爆誇大電器性能：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2010年調查指出<span style=\"color: red;\">冷氣效能誇大6.80%</span>，係眾多品牌中最跨！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今年調查發現，聲稱1級能源效益標籤嘅冷氣<span style=\"color: red;\">實際只係2級</span>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抽濕機每日抽濕量<span style=\"color: red;\">誇大11%</span>！<br />\n<br />\n依家日立電視機仲轉晒中國製添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！果然同CCTVB新聞一樣專講假話兼夾Made In China 呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n消委會報告：誇大製冷能力日立最誇 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36utT2K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36utT2K&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=754a5576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/36utT2K</a><br />\n八成窗口冷氣誇大製冷量 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/34sYnAn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34sYnAn&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=2c4f8c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/34sYnAn</a><br />\n日立抽濕機功能誇大11% - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Naw1Fq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Naw1Fq&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=8ef0a5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2Naw1Fq</a><br />\n日立電視機 madeinChina - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PFNdEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PFNdEw&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=df1a28ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2PFNdEw</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</stro